  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Comprehensive Action Plan for Afghanistan and Neighbouring Countries</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The crisis unfolding in Afghanistan is intensifying humanitarian needs and increasing displacement risks both inside the country, as well as across borders to neighbouring countries. Applying a regional migration lens to this crisis, IOM&#x2019;s Comprehensive Action Plan seeks to respond to humanitarian needs, whilst simultaneously mitigating the impact of the crisis in the region and supporting mid- and long-term support to affected persons, governments and societies for recovery and sustainable development.</narrative>
  </description>
